{"tid":615223,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食飯嚟講，環境定味道緊要？","createTime":"2018-04-03T07:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T20:16:46.000Z","uid":148609,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3376da1c3628ba5a9401281b4ac70282b9452fad","tid":615223,"uid":148609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"話說今日老豆同我去一間好似幾出名食雞翼豬扒飯嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n一去到見到公廁就喺隔離<br />\n枱面枱底勁多用過嘅紙巾未有人清<br />\n<br />\n一路食就望住伙計喺後巷倒廚餘同分碗碟<br />\n見到有迷你曱甴 仲聞到少少公廁味<br />\n<br />\n如果有兩個選擇<br />\n<br />\n一 太興嘅環境配一般味道嘅食物(唔好唔壞,接受到嘅程度)<br />\n<br />\n二 上述嘅環境配好好味食物<br />\n<br />\n你會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n示意圖(靜靜雞影係差啲)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/152849_c832a83ac30eb690d9257a0ab2022d0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F152849_c832a83ac30eb690d9257a0ab2022d0c.png&h=39296c28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e053736fdc1d7e91a8a9e18abe5ec2915d00a10","tid":615223,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"叫你係廁所入面食飯得唔得啊<br />\n問埋啲無謂野😑😑"},{"pid":"4caf62060044d8ef051d6ce38eee9fcfc73bc003","tid":615223,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb4001de0be7694c8088d24a82fdd9c9f1f18160","tid":615223,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f9ac3e397499b667049a11516f1c6766b2d9eeb","tid":615223,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"成記？ 勁正喎"},{"pid":"0bcb007cffbde61d4a234bcee04e50f6d237ef85","tid":615223,"uid":44814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"如果係咁我會外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲環境太差真係好影響食慾 去都唔會去"},{"pid":"9c8d48e6bbd9a7839a5c1b1cb2971f4b514c2bf1","tid":615223,"uid":148609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9ac3e397499b667049a11516f1c6766b2d9eeb","tid":615223,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:53:05.000Z","msg":"成記？ 勁正喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"係好味又大份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有機會我都係外賣算"},{"pid":"c8b3015b75d070ed05c5cfb0f47ef7bef5099986","tid":615223,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e053736fdc1d7e91a8a9e18abe5ec2915d00a10","tid":615223,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"叫你係廁所入面食飯得唔得啊<br />\n問埋啲無謂野😑😑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"之前咪有三條港女臭雞係台北廁所入面偷食鮑魚生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff13a7c229b4a37dead059bc51de94c41c49bdde","tid":615223,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"成記多數都外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9029563e5b5b0bd3efb19fa4efa1637d236b4a","tid":615223,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"太興嘅環境配一般味道嘅食物"},{"pid":"b2e7ebff679a1cdd57153b879df19e7affc24a5a","tid":615223,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"元朗？有個fd帶過我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過啲環境真係過分咗"},{"pid":"9d67f37931463d027838f561761f2ad1dd2534b4","tid":615223,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"話說有一年冬至 親戚介紹左一間係鴨脷洲叫 金寶做冬 點知 我食都無食 飲都無飲 因為我見到 佢d杯呀碗呀好似就咁搵水沖沖就算 然後俾下手用咁 勁多污積仲痴住係上面。仲有佢 連個地都濕濕地又黑黑地好似無拖過地咁 勁可怕😱 <br />\n我自問唔係要求高 但最基本衛生都做唔到 呢一間野唔使去都得，我真係情願食個三文治好過"},{"pid":"d5f90882251a9fbc2c5c53ea96d7e2a8a437bd25","tid":615223,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T20:11:35.000Z","msg":"其實環境會影響味道 所以冇得講"},{"pid":"e429603a756ca5a50b7ec19779b3e75a14ef8424","tid":615223,"uid":164523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T20:16:46.000Z","msg":"一諗到公廁就諗到成記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}